{"tid":1975571,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[NMSLESE]支那論壇NGA開始狗咬狗","createTime":"2020-04-16T15:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T12:07:53.000Z","uid":104216,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"caf7d221db9940697933b4a0b23074e1d0c21b48","tid":1975571,"uid":104216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:36:44.000Z","msg":"大家未必聽過nga <br />\n<br />\n亦都未必聽過一隻web game/app game叫gbf<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔重要<br />\n<br />\n可以睇到NMSLESE狗咬狗就忍唔住SHARE下<br />\n<br />\n事源係gbf呢隻game有個活動係30人對30人<br />\n<br />\n30人為之一團 或者你可以當佢係一個公會<br />\n<br />\n然後每日會抽一團黎鬥打高分咁<br />\n<br />\n咁今日有個台灣團抽到一個大陸團<br />\n<br />\n本身都無咩事 贏輸唔係好大影響<br />\n<br />\n咁今晚台灣團領先緊 唔知有心定無意啦<br />\n<br />\n將個團名改做 中國武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後對面支那團就緊係慶過火屎啦<br />\n<br />\n因為打唔贏 就諗住上支那壇NGA圍爐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHDVtBc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHDVtBc.jpg&h=7bdb3bbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJphGWd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJphGWd.jpg&h=35e868fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知冇幾耐 可能有D敏感詞 NGA版主就隱藏個post<br />\n<br />\n仲話「麻煩替論壇想一想好不好」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sfkkEJF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsfkkEJF.jpg&h=9b4e70a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vdjmpan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvdjmpan.jpg&h=a84c0143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁有部分有玩gbf既人都會留意下NGA gbf版既花生<br />\n<br />\n個支那團諗住改名還擊<br />\n<br />\n本身領先緊果個台灣團就瘋狂改名恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EMSWc43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMSWc43.jpg&h=322ae6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Z4hGYp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Z4hGYp.jpg&h=42238482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6b0XGYL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6b0XGYL.jpg&h=62f4e2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾發現唔夠人玩 改返原本個團名 可以幻想到佢地紅都面晒既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪覺得唔夠人地玩 就開始內哄<br />\n<br />\n覺得NGA版做乜唔係幫返自己人 反而要刪佢個post<br />\n<br />\n開始懷疑版主係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kUOyfjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkUOyfjF.jpg&h=bf2074ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XBsjaS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBsjaS0.jpg&h=8da599ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就有人唔憤氣係咁係nga版屌d版主<br />\n<br />\n然後版主就不斷秒刪post 但開post既人一定快過多過你刪<br />\n<br />\n西利既台灣玩家繼續開嘲諷技<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wjx7jNj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjx7jNj.jpg&h=917d3037&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q86zKd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq86zKd0.jpg&h=7a253eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後有班友嬲撚到 又咩都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n覺得點解對面團會咁清楚nga d post<br />\n<br />\n原來無知到以為佢地只可以睇牆內野 所以外人都睇唔到佢地牆內既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有人嬲撚到舉報埋個壇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZSftKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZSftKK.jpg&h=8767ce17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R9qpm4L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR9qpm4L.jpg&h=7b0c0afb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MXW74if.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMXW74if.jpg&h=3e9a86f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事態發展得太快 我一路打呢個post都一路有好多新進展 我都跟唔切<br />\n<br />\n但再一次證明牆內人d邏輯真係特別過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n太多花生食唔晒 暫時睇到最新一篇公告笑出聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXO6AqW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXO6AqW.jpg&h=929538e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理<br />\n<br />\n性<br />\n<br />\n愛<br />\n<br />\n國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家佢地開始討論緊點樣同營運投訴辱華<br />\n<br />\n一路執腸一路跟進<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝台灣網友既出力<br />\n<br />\n可以搞到人地地盤狗咬狗 西利過TAIWAN NO.1！"},{"pid":"e47e0bb6a89051ccf894e55e7a67e180f16a2fc0","tid":1975571,"uid":90521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"最正就係全程都係打輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"493a9092458814c8278e7257da133b14a14ef3b5","tid":1975571,"uid":104216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47e0bb6a89051ccf894e55e7a67e180f16a2fc0","tid":1975571,"uid":90521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"最正就係全程都係打輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"每日要打到夜晚11點先完<br />\n<br />\n版主心諗你班仆街比我打埋先得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed24a500c5fef16334bf575a8c6cc0e4c015749","tid":1975571,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"493a9092458814c8278e7257da133b14a14ef3b5","tid":1975571,"uid":104216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47e0bb6a89051ccf894e55e7a67e180f16a2fc0","tid":1975571,"uid":90521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"最正就係全程都係打輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:44:35.000Z","msg":"每日要打到夜晚11點先完<br />\n<br />\n版主心諗你班仆街比我打埋先得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:49:31.000Z","msg":"唔知兒登班支那仔點睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8256e4d2ab0e21fa99f0779527f92497e5d881ad","tid":1975571,"uid":222795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />理性愛國呢啲term 真係全世界得支那先會用"},{"pid":"7d06a610b669ab63049984a7ef4f9355a48b299b","tid":1975571,"uid":201182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:02:16.000Z","msg":"屌 好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbb8b330c1596830870135437d6bcdb151002fc","tid":1975571,"uid":104216,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"GBF事件簡易懶人包<br />\n1. 支那人 被 中國武漢肺炎團 打爆<br />\n2. 氣到跑去中國論壇NGA哭哭取暖<br />\n3. 結果遭版主刪文<br />\n4. 質疑管理方有台灣的內鬼<br />\n5. 事情正式爆發 大量文章出現<br />\n6. 版主繼續大量刪文 引爆民怨 甚至向國家舉報該網站<br />\n7. 版主出面解釋：我知道你們很生氣 但是你們貼的那些資料有太多敏感資料<br />\n 如果我不刪除 論壇會面臨危險<br />\n8. 版友不買單：那你一開始就說清楚 幹嘛鬼鬼祟祟的一直刪文?<br />\n 更何況這是國家尊嚴的問題 你身為版主不保護國家尊嚴還刪我們文!<br />\n9. 版主繼續委婉地暗示：黨說我們不可以翻牆 不可以跟外國人玩遊戲<br />\n 你們不要這麼張揚....&larr;現在在這裡<br />\n<br />\n好想見到GBF變成一隻無支那狗玩既GAME"},{"pid":"4b52dcaca2aee6d441e4460fa33425a5654ab8d0","tid":1975571,"uid":104216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wnTKnpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwnTKnpt.jpg&h=f38aec17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n快撚D炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6d97cebe84a43e651c5f0b9567bf81f576ebd9","tid":1975571,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4c8d998d3a666d3acef7e3370178c035c2211e","tid":1975571,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"支那狗真係攞來賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9f084aa8814e060de70b9f98acdc670f63a7db","tid":1975571,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9c4b4a8976361bcc0983f0e52c785959cf2284c","tid":1975571,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e9c3342c854b6eba8771c4f749012120172af5","tid":1975571,"uid":104216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:46:50.000Z","msg":"最新update<br />\n<br />\n因為遊戲歸遊戲政治歸政治的迴力鏢打到自己身上<br />\n<br />\n版主被扣了一個4v內鬼的帽子之後發了一個反串帖<br />\n<br />\n假裝自己是肺炎團的人 發了id出來招人 實際上是想指路讓人去搗亂<br />\n<br />\n結果粉蛆們看不懂 把這截圖大肆宣揚抓到版主是台毒的證據<br />\n<br />\n於是開始微博擴散 瘋狂檢舉<br />\n<br />\n手遊瓜版關閉 粉蛆們流到其他版面鬧<br />\n<br />\n但根據政治歸政治 遊戲歸遊戲 傑尼龜傑尼的原則 nga禁談政治<br />\n<br />\n於是繼續刪帖<br />\n<br />\n最後發現勢不可擋<br />\n<br />\nnga全 站 禁 言<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuX7kDx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuX7kDx.jpg&h=932d370e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOYRNiy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOYRNiy.jpg&h=ff0f97ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd5dcfe7851902e966f840b4910165373ea95924","tid":1975571,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:49:53.000Z","msg":"咁長城封左GBF未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd955c72feb4b371a3bf1d19a5c8ed273919319","tid":1975571,"uid":2192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:51:30.000Z","msg":"GBF以為係gundam build fighter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4501